<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Read and Write Latencies>
We are investigating elevated latencies for read and write requests for AWS Storage Gateway in the US-WEST-2 Region.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Read and Write Latencies>
We have identified the cause of elevated latencies for read and write requests for AWS Storage Gateway in the US-WEST-2 Region and continue working towards resolution.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased Read and Write Latencies>
Between 6:18 AM and 8:06 AM PST we experienced elevated latencies for read and write requests for AWS Storage Gateway in the US-WEST-2 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
